    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 1993 Mazda RX-7 features the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power through its factory 5-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains exceptionally balanced with its front-midship engine placement and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension. Recent maintenance includes a full cooling system overhaul and inspection of the vacuum line 'rat\u2019s nest' to ensure consistent boost patterns. Equipped with a Torsen limited-slip differential, this FD provides visceral feedback and precise turn-in. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the compression remains strong across both rotors, and the drivetrain is mechanically sound.",
