    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between executive luxury and athletic performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with highway driving. It sits on 19-inch multi-spoke alloy wheels wrapped in tires with excellent tread remaining. Inside, the Dakota leather interior is in wonderful shape; the seats are supple and the cabin still carries that premium BMW scent, with only very slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every technological feature, from the iDrive infotainment system with navigation to the Harman Kardon surround sound, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is top-tier. It has been serviced strictly at authorized intervals, with a full folder of receipts available for review. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six engine provides smooth, effortless power, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garage-kept and loved. It offers the peace of mind of a brand-new car at a significantly more accessible price point.",
