    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This driver-focused example boasts a 3.64 limited-slip differential and factory-spec individual throttle bodies for immediate throttle response. The chassis maintains its integrity with precise MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent VANOS system check and valve adjustment to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains accessible. While the paint presents minor patina typical of a well-enjoyed enthusiast vehicle, the structural components and drivetrain remain in excellent working order.",
